      "content": "That's a heavy realization, but it's also a sign that you've finally stopped running and started facing the truth. The world doesn't need an endless itinerary to be worth experiencing; it's just that you've exhausted the parts of yourself that were looking for new things to chase. Maybe the only thing left to do now is to sit with the silence and let the ocean remind you that you don't need to keep moving to be whole.",
